Validation Rule 1

Rule Name:
Employee_Name_Validation

Formula:
LEN(Name) < 3

Error Message:
Employee Name must contain at least 3 characters.



Validation Rule 2

Rule Name:
Employee_ID_Validation

Formula:
EmpId__c <= 0

Error Message:
Employee ID must be greater than 0.


Validation Rule 3

Rule Name:
Salary_Validation

Formula:
OR(
    Salary__c <= 10000,
    Salary__c >= 500000
)

Error Message:
Salary must be between 10,000 and 500,000.



Validation Rule 4

Rule Name:
Department_Validation

Formula:
ISBLANK(TEXT(Dept__c))

Error Message:
Please select Department.



Validation Rule 5

Rule Name:
Joining_Date_Validation

Formula:
JoiningDate__c > TODAY()

Error Message:
Joining Date cannot be a future date.



Note:
Email field validation is automatically handled by Salesforce because Email__c field type is Email.